quran[10]{c,v,t}:
  17,61,"wadhkur qawluna llmlaykt: asjuduu liadam tahiatan wtkrymana, fasajaduu jmyeana 'iilaa 'iblys, astakbar waimtanae ean alsujud qayla ealaa sabil al'inkar walastkbar: 'a'asjud lhdha aldeyf, almkhlwq min altyn?"
  17,62,"wqal 'iiblis jra't ealaa allah wkfrana bh: 'ara'ayt hdha almkhlwq aldhy myzth elya? layin abqytny hyana 'iilaa yawm alqiamat lastwlynn ealaa dhuriyatah bal'ighwa' wal'ifsad, 'iilaa almukhlasin minhum fi al'iyman, wahum qlyl"
  17,63,"qal allah taealaa mhddana 'iiblis watbaeh: adhhab fman tabieak min dhuriyat adm, fataek, fa'iina eqabk weqabhm wafr fi nar jhnm"
  17,64,"wastakhfif kl man tastatie astkhfafh minhum bdewtk 'iiaah 'iilaa mesyty, wa'ajmae ealayhim kl ma taqdir ealayh min jnwdk min kuli rakb wrajl, wajeal lnfsk shirkt fi 'amwalihim bi'ana yksbwha min alhram, wshirkt fi alawlad btzyyn alzna walmeasy, wmkhalft 'awamir allah hataa ykthr alfjwr walfsad, weid atbaek min dhuriyat adam alwewd alkadhbt, fkl wueud alshaytan batlt wghrwr"
  17,65,"'in eibadi almuminin almukhlasin aladhin ataewny lays lak qudrat ealaa 'ighwayhm, wakafaa birabik -ayha alnby- easmana whafzana lilmuminin min kayd alshaytan wghrwrh"
  17,66,rbkm -ayha alnas- hu aldhy yusayir lakum alsufun fi albhr; lttlbu rizq allah fi asfarkm wtjaratkm. 'iina allah subhanah kan rhymana bebadh
  17,67,"w'idha 'asabatkum shdt fi albahr hataa ashrftm ealaa algharaq walhlak, ghab ean eqwlkm aladhin tebdwnhm min alalht, wtdhkkartm allah alqadir whdh; lyghythkm wynqdhkm, fakhlstm lah fi talab aleawn wal'ighatht, faghathkm wnjjakm, flmma najaakum 'iilaa albari 'aeradtum ean al'iiman wal'iikhlas waleamal alsalh, whdha min jahl al'iinsan wkfrh. wakan al'iinsan jhwdana lnem allah ezz wjl"
  17,68,"aghafaltm -ayha alnas- ean eadhab allh, famntm 'ana tanhar bikum al'ard khsfana, 'aw yumtrkm allah bihijarat min alsama' ftqtlkm, thuma la tajiduu ahdana yhfzkm min edhabh?"
  17,69,"am 'amintum -ayha alnas- rbkm, waqad kafartum bih 'an yueidakum fi albahr maratan akhra, fayursil ealaykum ryhana shdydt, tkssir kl ma 'atat elyh, fayughriqakum bsbb kfrkm, thuma la tajiduu lakum ealayna 'aya tbet wmtalbt; fa'iina allah lm yzlmkm mithqal dhr?"
  17,70,"wlqd krramna dhuriyat adam baleql wa'iirsal alrsl, wsakhkharna lahum jmye ma fi alkwn, wsakhkharna lahum aldawabi fi albari walsfn fi albahr lhmlhm, warazaqnahum min tayibat almataeim walmsharb, wfddalnahm ealaa kthyr min almkhlwqat tafdilana ezymana"